{"tid":1919693,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「成績表！」我地一齊like香港黑警個page 早日突破40萬 2.0","createTime":"2020-03-11T03:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T04:56:11.000Z","uid":277186,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c96648a5aee211436fcbf73ed6a3bd552a2fdf8a","tid":1919693,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"我地一齊like香港黑警個page 早日突破40萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1918074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1918074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n話說琴日9點開左個post☝🏻 <br />\n24小時後：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvdMTOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvdMTOO.png&h=cff184d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由7萬人爆升至24萬的確可喜可賀！<br />\n<br />\n先多謝各位連登仔幫手推post <br />\np牌推唔到post無力感真係好重 一日又開得一個 有咁既效果真係好滾動<br />\n<br />\n講明先，個page唔係我own的 我只係幫手宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n廢話唔多講，like page依個post點解我會follow得咁緊要呢，其實可以從細節睇到今時今日香港人諗緊咩<br />\n大部分都心態正面 非常好，唔多評論。以下同大家分析下post內<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">負面</span></span>留言。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警告⚠️以下內容涉及偷換概念。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npiQA6C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpiQA6C.png&h=521b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，facebook有審查有機會del page，但係請問同你like page有咩關係？你只可以俾一個like？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">假如該行動對抗爭運動有正面幫助 撐左先啦</span>唔好一味覺得依樣唔得個樣唔得<br />\n行動有正面幫助 自己適合該次行動 -&gt; 身體力行<br />\n行動有正面幫助 自己不適合該次行動 -&gt; 送上支持或有用意見即可<br />\n連登仔唔係弱智架，除非係專業意見（例如整熄TG要用鹽）<br />\n否則你諗到其他人都諗到 你唔駛懶係醒去將最並差情況講出黎 自己會衡量的<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多一點鼓勵 少一點批評</span><br />\n- - - -<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzB3bEY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzB3bEY.png&h=0dc36c3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTusDjY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTusDjY.png&h=0947aca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">做人唔好船頭驚鬼 船尾驚賊啦</span><br />\n用下個腦諗下係咪真係會因為你like個page而上門拉你<br />\n告你d咩？ like page犯法嗎？正如我去周梓樂既悼念活動都無犯法的<br />\n- - - -<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cZcPrF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cZcPrF.png&h=23a6c4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4CK0Yj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4CK0Yj1.png&h=36ae27b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅字係同一個人☝🏻<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你知唔知紅色加超大其實好撚討厭？</span></span><br />\n套落現實生活=你一邊手舞足蹈一邊大叫 同隻紅色狒狒係無咩分別。只要你有道理就有人聽<br />\n同埋唔需要分港豬唔港豬，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好強行將負面形容詞套落任何一個同路人身上</span><br />\n網絡世界人人平等，我唔識你你唔識我，你無資格去將人分門別類 謝謝<br />\n政治係加減法，多一點朋友少一點敵人，基本上上得連登既都係黃絲，<span style=\"color: red;\">分門別類係內部分化既開始</span><br />\n只要目標一致即可<br />\n人地唔想做 唔記得左做 唔知道要做咪下次囉 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好強逼他人與你苦難行軍及放大一d無撚聊既事</span><br />\n- - - -<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKf3V6G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKf3V6G.png&h=a34ab91c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下內容適合全部文宣頻道。<br />\n<br />\n依個問題其實同市場供求係一樣，8個月黎有千千萬萬個page tg谷，市場上供應已過盛。<br />\n問下你 facebook一格screen可以show幾多個post? 係1個 <br />\n一日瀏覽Facebook嘅在線時間係幾多？一個小時夠多啦掛？<br />\n以上邊網媒winandmac media做例子 同類資訊我可能係立場新聞 蘋果已經睇左，我點解要睇你先？<br />\n最重要既係獨特性，與其出現重複性資訊導致觀眾盲目，<span style=\"color: red;\">諗個理由令觀眾一定要睇你</span><br />\n<br />\n又或者竟然想出一分力 但效果不如其他文宣頻道，<span style=\"color: red;\">倒不如大家合組，細group+細group變大group</span><br />\n可令資訊集中以及令同類觀眾困在你既頻道減少分散流失<br />\n<br />\n搶眼球都係做文宣既重點之一，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實每個人生活上都有唔同嘅壓力</span><br />\n認清一個事實， 有趣（funny)內容係網絡世界最hit既content，好多人拎起電話都係想鬆一鬆。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮用什麼方式去表達比內容更重要</span><br />\n<br />\n最後就係<span style=\"color: red;\">做文宣要有明確目的！</span> 點解黑警page可以一下爆上24萬？<br />\n咪因為警察page個30萬thx 我地黃絲要超越佢，就係咁簡單<br />\n假如無「30萬thx」個post，d人睇完haha就算，唔會有下文的。 <span style=\"color: red;\">順勢操作很重要</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8wVWxbo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wVWxbo.png&h=6b28758a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打左2個鐘 page又上升至25萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望page主好好珍惜啦"},{"pid":"599b8ffd8b28c806b226827168230535d1de84fc","tid":1919693,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"Done"},{"pid":"7759c198d8cd240ba3f8b0a0f4c405f6bc9927c3","tid":1919693,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"香港黑警page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-Hong-Kong-Popo-112773503486936/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-Hong-Kong-Popo-112773503486936%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=a28af03c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-Hong-Kong-Popo-112773503486936/</a>"},{"pid":"3487fee6f98c457423084fdc2ead361d3951a372","tid":1919693,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"05b57ac9d8062d2716ddb159d16c26bd7eed140a","tid":1919693,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"787299cf2f964fc627a8f9dfff2db2659ad2e717","tid":1919693,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:20:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47c823650465243f42016c41bd80b7149a0ec932","tid":1919693,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7146cdac4aa